abstract: Florida woman shoots her adult daughter to death after mistaking her for intruder.
lead_paragraph: A mother in Central Florida mistook her daughter for an intruder and shot her to death, the police said Wednesday.

headline.main: Florida: Woman Accidentally Kills Daughter, Police Say
